snippet.title: Asmodeus's Hell: Devil in the Sunshine State Trailer
snippet.description:
Kowechobe is a town infamous for occult activity and supernatural occurrences. Khyle Romano has spent his entire life avoiding this part of his hometown, but slowly finds himself tied into something sinister while trying to pursue the girl of his dreams.

'Asmodeus's Hell: Devil in the Sunshine State' is coming  2022!
Be sure to follow me on itch.io for updates: https://pekoxpoke.itch.io/?msclkid=fb556381ad0e11ec960d36e5eecb26dd

Song: "I'm Not the Girl” by Rachel Farris, licensed by Triple Scoop Music
Sound effect: https://freesound.org/people/newlocknew/
